  <p>
    Btw, this is a link with an explanation of what pequi is. It is in one of the Brazilian chicken dishes. I guess it might answer my quetion about the part of Brazil the owners might come from - Goiás<br/><br/>Link: <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pequi" target="_blank">http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pequi</a><br/><br/>Image: <a href="http://milmaisuma.leiturascom.net/arquivo/pequi2.jpg" target="_blank">http://milmaisuma.leiturascom.net/arquivo/pequi2.jpg</a>
